quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,121,"∆Āe mbi'i : "min ngooŇč…óinii Jey…óo winndere ndeen,"
  7,122,"Joomum Muusaa e Haaruuna"."
  7,123,"Fir'awna wi'i : "On ngooŇč…óini mo adii mi mi yamirde= sakkitoore on? Pellet, …óuum …óoo ko fewjoore nde pewju…óon ka saare fii no njaltiniron toon yim…ďe mayre. ma on nganndu."
  7,124,"Ma mi ta∆īa juu…óe mon …óen e koy…óe mon …óeen (mi) luutindira, refti ma mi feta on denndaangal"."
  7,125,"∆Āe mbi'i : "minen, ko faade ka Joomi amen woni ruttorde amen."
  7,126,"A a√Īiraani min si wanaa fii min ngooŇč…óinii maandeeji Joomi amen, tuma nde …ói ngarunoo amen. Joomi amen! Yuppu mu√Īal e amen, ∆īettitaa min ko min jebbilii …ďe.(juul…ďe)"
  7,127,"Mbatu yim…ďe Fir'awna ngun mbi'i : "A accat Muusaa e yim…ďe mum …ďeen no bonnira ka leydi, o acce an e dewetee…ói maa …óin?!" o wi'i : "ma min mbar …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen men ngaccita …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen (nguura). Pellet, minen, e dow ma…ď…ďe ko min fooloo…ďe"."
  7,128,"Muusaa maakani yim…ďe makko …ďeen : "mballinoree Alla mu√Ī√Īo…óon. Pellet, leydi ndin ka Alla woodani, Himo ronina ndi on mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. battane mo∆ī∆īe …óeen ko gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen woodani"."
  7,129,"∆Āe mbi'i : "min lorranooma adii a arde amen e …ďaawo nde ngar…óaa e amen". O maaki : "Hino jortaa nde Joomi mon halkata ga√Īo mon O lomtina on ka leydi, O ndaara ko holno ngollirton"."
  7,130,"GooŇč…óii min nanngirii yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe kokke e usytagol …ďesnooje ; mbelejo'o, …ďe mbaajitoto."